native\n   113\t- Hard caps: `maxContracts`, `maxPositionPct` of portfolio\n   1
14\t\n   115\t### 5.3 Risk Manager (`risk-manager.js`)\n   116\tEnforces guardra
ils:\n   117\t- Minimum confidence & edge thresholds\n   118\t- Max daily loss l
imit\n   119\t- Cooldown per market\n   120\t- Max exposure per market\n   121\t
\n   122\t### 5.4 P&L Tracker (in `index.js`)\n   123\t- Tracks open/closed posi
tions\n   124\t- Computes realized & unrealized P&L\n   125\t- Calculates Sharpe
ratio, win rate, max drawdown\n   126\t- Emits events for position open/close\n 
 127\t\n   128\t### 5.5 Strategy Runner (`runner.js`)\n   129\t- Fetches active 
markets + portfolio\n   130\t- Runs all registered strategies\n   131\t- Applies
