xploits cross-platform price spreads |\n   144\t| **Mean Reversion** | `mean-rev
ersion-strategy.js` | Trades toward 0.50 when price > 0.80 or < 0.20 |\n   145\t
\n   146\t---\n   147\t\n   148\t## 7. Example Strategy: Mean Reversion\n   149\
t\n   150\t**Logic:**\n   151\t- If `impliedProbability > 0.80`, signal `sell_ye
s` (buy NO, revert to 0.50)\n   152\t- If `impliedProbability < 0.20`, signal `b
uy_yes` (revert to 0.50)\n   153\t- Confidence scales with distance from 0.50\n 
 154\t\n   155\t**Position sizing:**\n   156\t- Uses Kelly criterion via `BaseSt
